<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_137_r1l4"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> vıcʒtum als Jr vns 
<add><ab facs="#facs_137_r1l3"><expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan> </ab></add> <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt wıe Jr mıt vveinmar <expan>Ek<ex>er</ex></expan> gerett </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_137_r1l5">vnd beſtellet habt daʒ er <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> frıd mıt vns <expan>halte<ex>n</ex></expan> well bıs auf den <expan>ſun<ex>n</ex>tag</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_137_r1l6">Acht tag nach dem <expan>heılıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>Oſt<ex>er</ex>tag</expan> ſchıerıſt . wan Jr in der <expan>v<ex>er</ex>gangen</expan> ʒeıt niht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_137_r1l7">müſſıg <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ſeyt tag ʒu <expan>beſchaıd<ex>en</ex></expan> etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_137_r1l8"><expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>fleıſſıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> . daʒ Jr eẅch in den <expan>ſach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> alſo müet / Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_137_r1l9">wıewol vvır mıt dem <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> vveınmar <expan>Ek<ex>er</ex></expan> niht <expan>wıſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu ſchıken <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> . denn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_137_r1l10">guts . So <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır doch mıt Jm vnd den <expan>ſeıne<ex>n</ex></expan> ein gütlıch ſteen <expan>halt<ex>en</ex></expan> für </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_137_r1l11">vns vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> on <expan>geu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> bıs auf den <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> ſunntag acht tag nach dem </ab>
