<ab facs="#facs_137_r1l14">laſſe . wan wır <expan>hoff<ex>en</ex></expan> Jr verſteet ſelbs wol daʒ er vns <expan>ſölıch<ex>er</ex></expan> ſprüch wol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_137_r1l15"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>trüg</expan> . Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ij<hi rend="sup">a</hi></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_137_r1l16"><expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> Letare </ab>
